dalvik-explorer/src/org/jessies/dalvikexplorer/BuildActivity.java: avoid verification failures on Android 1.5 devices:

  D/dalvikvm(  751): DexOpt: couldn't find static field
  W/dalvikvm(  751): VFY: unable to resolve static field 5 (MANUFACTURER) in Landroid/os/Build;
  W/dalvikvm(  751): VFY:  rejecting opcode 0x62 at 0x0019
  W/dalvikvm(  751): VFY:  rejected Lorg/jessies/dalvikexplorer/BuildActivity;.getBuildDetailsAsString ()Ljava/lang/String;
  W/dalvikvm(  751): Verifier rejected class Lorg/jessies/dalvikexplorer/BuildActivity;
  W/dalvikvm(  751): Class init failed in newInstance call (Lorg/jessies/dalvikexplorer/BuildActivity;)

The CPU_ABI and MANUFACTURER fields were added to android.os.Build in Android 1.6, so we can't access them directly if we want to run on pre-1.6 devices.


